{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"57307-chakula-hayawani","title":"Chakula Hayawani","description":"Kutoka kwa mkate wa roti hadi samosa na chakili hadi mkate wa barfi, kuna aina mbalimbali ya vyakula unaweza tumia inchini Hindi. Lakini umewai kufikiria kuhusu umbo la hivi vyakula?","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rachel Andisi"],"illustrators":["Aindri C"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/57307-chakula-hayawani"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/123549/size3/3687d0df50d079218bf3867d505dcd51.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/123549/size6/3687d0df50d079218bf3867d505dcd51.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53010/size6/acb69406e89ded65e663d49f2357de64.jpg","text":"Mkate wa roti ni wa  \n            mviringo.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52565/size6/da1e615e18e63dea02f15fe74abf3b21.jpg","text":"Mkate wa pakoda ni wa pembe tatu.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52554/size6/f7807a5c025627b99aa646077157dd37.jpg","text":"Mkate wa aina wa barfi ni wa mraba.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53008/size6/800ef77249546c5d03d9783ee20e8208.jpg","text":"Mkate wa Chakili ni wa msokoto.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52557/size6/f637417743b18e2fbd22ef1904c5c56e.jpg","text":"Mkate wa Kachori ni  kama pete .","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53011/size6/998445c33e886f1d4e1447a300e7d80d.jpg","text":"Mkate wa kuku siagi ni wa  silinda.\nMkate wa kuku siagi ni chakula kitamu cha Kibungala ambacho kimetengenezwa kutoka kwa unga uliosafishwa, ukaongezwa nazi na sukuri nguuru.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52566/size6/bf5d2db61c496d725d837f66b13de98c.jpg","text":"Mkate wa Pomfreti ni wa pembe sita,\n                                           ukikatwa katikati.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53012/size6/6bc14c420440b9bfc9e693a2b951351d.jpg","text":"Mkate wa samosa ni wa pia,\n                                     ukunjwa kutoka mwisho.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52568/size6/5337bd65421d2d3fda6bab1ea403dd62.jpg","text":"Mkate wa Halua hauna umbo.\n                                            Huchukua umbo ambalo umeipatia.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52562/size6/fee101d2cbb716c5aacde7edcfaf6fdf.jpg","text":"Yote huja pamoja na kuwa\nchakula hayawani.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52563/size6/fa0d9edb1792a6cb700bc132b73c90d1.jpg","text":"Natafuta chakula hayawani\nkwa sahani.\nNa kuila na wengu, uhaba, tata na kidoko!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":108}}